c: 6
v: 25
t: "Harimwo muribo abakwumviriza natwe twashizeho inzitizi mumitima yabo, kugira ngo ntibaze bayamenye ayo majambo bumva, kandi nuko hari uruzitiro ruri mumatwi yabo, rero babonye ivyemezo vyacu ntiba vyemera naho baje guharira na wewe bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baca bavuga bati:- ibi vyose nta nakimwe kirimwo atari imigani gusa y’abantu bakera"